result.title: The Family Circumstances of the Irregular Witch
result.description:
Alyssa, a witch who lives alone in the woods, finds a human baby one day. Despite her bewilderment, she names the child Viola and decides to raise her. 16 years later, Viola has grown far more than Alissa ever imagined... Wait, she grew too much! And so, the chaotic comedy of a mother and daughter with inverted appearances begins!! (Source: Crunchyroll)

User rating: 96%
